data.description: Veterans this is a Great Opportunity for you! VA Assumable loan at 2.25%. This 4 bed 2 bath home is located in the coveted neighborhood of Stockwell Place!  When you walk through the door you will love the Gorgous flooring throughout the home and open floor plan. The Primary bedroom is remote with an ensuite bath, large walk in closet, separate shower and jetted tub. Beautiful kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, gas cooktop, and granite countertops. Walk out the back door to a screened in porch facing a large private fenced in yard with no back yard neighbors! Large wood storage shed in back for lawn equipment, tools, and more. Schedule your private showing today, don't let this one get away!
